1
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:06,000
(Sound of electrocardiogram monitor)

2
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:09,000
(ECG monitor alarm)

3
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:13,000
(Kiryu Subaru) One cylinder of adrenaline

4
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:13,000
Shot every 4 minutes.

5
00:00:13,000 --> 00:00:15,000
(Akira Aoyama) Yes.

6
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:17,000
Pulse check.

7
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:17,000
(light) Yes.

8
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:19,000
(Light) My heartbeat hasn't returned!

9
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:23,000
It's VF. I'm going to DC. Set to 150!

10
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:23,000
(light) Yes.

11
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:28,000
(Grandson) Grandpa! Grandpa!

12
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:28,000
Mr. Akai, child, please let go!

13
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:30,000
(Shiori Akai) Yes! Because it's okay. Hey?

14
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:35,000
(ECG monitor alarm)

15
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:38,000
(Ambulance siren)

16
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:41,000
(Male) It hurts, it hurts, it hurts, it hurts...!

17
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:44,000
Ah! It hurts, it hurts, it hurts, it hurts, it hurts!

18
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:44,000
It hurts, it hurts, it hurts, it hurts…!

19
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:47,000
(Yui Kuronuma) Please don't move!

20
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:47,000
(Takeshi Momoyama) Oh wait...!

21
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:50,000
I can see the bones!

22
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:50,000
(Momoyama) Huh? Ah! It's true.

23
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:52,000
Is this the second metacarpal? Is it the third one?

24
00:00:52,000 --> 00:00:54,000
(Mie Toyama) Yes, yes, don't move!

25
00:00:54,000 --> 00:00:57,000
“Muscles don’t betray you!” right?

26
00:00:54,000 --> 00:00:57,000
(Male) Yes...

27
00:00:57,000 --> 00:01:01,000
(Shozo Gonno) Mie-chan

28
00:00:57,000 --> 00:01:01,000
A chest trauma patient?

29
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:05,000
(Mie) An unexpected doctor heard about the symptoms.

30
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:05,000
I said it was impossible!

31
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:09,000
If you don't accept it, don't let it get carried away.

32
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:09,000
Right? What's going on?

33
00:01:09,000 --> 00:01:12,000
Isn't it Haruka-chan?

34
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:16,000
(Mie) Mr. Haruki is off duty.

35
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:16,000
It was the wedding of a classmate from medical school!

36
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:18,000
(Nasu Nasu) Back okay!

37
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:20,000
(Teru Shibukawa) Remove.

38
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:22,000
Tatsuya Yamashiro, 35 years old, male.

39
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:24,000
hit by a car

40
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:24,000
There are trauma marks on the head and chest.

41
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:28,000
Cardiopulmonary arrest was confirmed in the car.

42
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:28,000
They administered CPR, AED and intubation.

43
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:31,000
Were you intubated without permission?

44
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:31,000
Medical Control Who?

45
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:33,000
What are the instructions for transportation to my house?

46
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:36,000
(Haruki Haruki) Yes, yes, yes, yes! It's me!

47
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:40,000
(Mie) Mr. Haruki!?

48
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:40,000
Haruka-chan, are you going to work in an ambulance?

49
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:42,000
I just happened to be at the scene.

50
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:45,000
(Shibukawa) Stretcher passing!

51
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:49,000
(Mie) An unexpected teacher says it's impossible.

52
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:49,000
Mr. Haruki, can you do it!?

53
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:53,000
As long as you're with Kiryu-sensei, you'll be fine!

54
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:53,000
Subaru is treating a patient in cardiopulmonary arrest.

55
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:55,000
Huh!?

56
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:58,000
(Mie) It's not "Eh!?"!

57
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:58,000
What should I do if I accept it without permission?

58
00:01:58,000 --> 00:02:02,000
I'll do it alone!

59
00:01:58,000 --> 00:02:02,000
Mie-san, please prepare for the surgery!

60
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:05,000
Hey! Can the heart break? Haruka-chan.

61
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:09,000
I've never done it before.

62
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:09,000
But if someone doesn't do it, you'll die!

63
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:11,000
Right?

64
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:17,000
♬〜

65
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:31,000
♬〜

66
00:02:31,000 --> 00:02:33,000
(Hiroto Mashima) Ugh...

67
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:39,000
♬〜

68
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:41,000
(Mashima) Are you okay!?

69
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:48,000
(Ring tone)

70
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:51,000
📞(Communications dispatcher) This is Kanagawa Prefectural Police.

71
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:51,000
Is it an incident? Was it an accident?

72
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:55,000
(Mashima) I'm sorry. I hit someone with my car.

73
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:57,000
It's covered in blood... What should I do!?

74
00:02:58,000 --> 00:03:00,000
(Shibukawa) Itadakimasu.

75
00:02:58,000 --> 00:03:00,000
(Nasu/Yutaka Hanamaki) Itadakimasu.

76
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:04,000
(Hanamaki) Nasu You

77
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:04,000
Don't you want to qualify as a lifeguard?

78
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:09,000
(Nasu) Well... I can get it.

79
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:09,000
Isn't it just responsibility and a badge?

80
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:14,000
Tsk... You don't have any aspirations.

81
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:14,000
Hey? Shibukawa.

82
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:18,000
No, I'm still a long way from being a lifesaver.

83
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:18,000
The great thing is...

84
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:21,000
(Nasu) Tell me, you're the captain.

85
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:21,000
You don't have any qualifications, do you?

86
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:23,000
(Hanamaki) Huh?

87
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:23,000
Fufufufufufu…!

88
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:25,000
(command tone)

89
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:27,000
I'm coming.

90
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:30,000
🔊(Command Controller) is the first to appear for rescue.

91
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:34,000
🔊Hakuocho 7-chome signalized intersection.

92
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:39,000
🔊(Radio) From Yokohama Minato Police Station to Kannai Higashi Police Box.

93
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:39,000
Directive number 1285.

94
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:41,000
(Kento Yokomine) I'm going first!

95
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:44,000
(Iwao Tachikawa) Hey, Yokomine! So much...! Ahhh...!

96
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:46,000
(Tachikawa) Yokomine Wait a minute!

97
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:50,000
(Yokomine) Alright! Okay...!

98
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:50,000
(Tachikawa) Hey hey hey! a little bit…!

99
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:52,000
(Hanamaki) Alright! let's go.

100
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:52,000
(Nasu) Understood!

101
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:57,000
(sound of engine starting)

102
00:03:57,000 --> 00:04:02,000
(Ambulance siren)

103
00:03:57,000 --> 00:04:02,000
(fire engine siren)

104
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:05,000
(Nasu) Just go straight like this.

105
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:05,000
Pier Street is spinning!

106
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:08,000
(Hanamaki) No, avoid the Ashikamachi intersection.

107
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:08,000
Guard Down It would be faster to go south.

108
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:10,000
Yes!

109
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:10,000
(Shibukawa) Can you stop the bleeding with pressure?

110
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:12,000
I'll try it! What should I do!?

111
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:17,000
Handkerchief Towel Use as clean a cloth as possible

112
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:17,000
Apply pressure to the bleeding area.

113
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:23,000
ᗒ(Ambulance siren)

114
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:23,000
(Mashima) I'm sorry... I'm sorry...

115
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:30,000
♬〜

116
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:32,000
(Shibukawa) Thank you!

117
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:34,000
Ah... I'm sorry!

118
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:40,000
(Moderator) Next number

119
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:40,000
Let the bride and groom lead you.

120
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:43,000
(MC) Jean!

121
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:43,000
(2 people) Episode 9!

122
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:45,000
(Moderator) It's number 9! 1 digit number 9!

123
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:48,000
Oh!

124
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:48,000
It seems like a lot of people are open.

125
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:54,000
(Rui Togawa)Haruka! Haven't you been drinking?

126
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:56,000
Yeah. I might be on call.

127
00:04:56,000 --> 00:05:01,000
(Rui) Even at times like this, I think about work.

128
00:04:56,000 --> 00:05:01,000
I can't believe it.

129
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:06,000
Hey Haruka

130
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:06,000
Why did you choose such a tedious rescue?

131
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:10,000
To simply save people?

132
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:13,000
(3 people laughing)

133
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:16,000
Are you coming?

134
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:19,000
There's no overtime on duty, and the pay is higher than now.

135
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:22,000
Hey! Seriously?

136
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:28,000
But I'll stop.

137
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:28,000
I want to save lives.

138
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:33,000
If only I could straighten my sense of justice

139
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:33,000
It must feel good.

140
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:37,000
ᗒ(Ambulance siren)

141
00:05:33,000 --> 00:05:37,000
ᗒ(fire engine siren)

142
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:43,000
It's close. There's also a pump.

143
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:43,000
(Female) Pump? A fire engine?

144
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:46,000
I'll leave first.

145
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:49,000
Huh... where are you going?

146
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:53,000
I'll show off my sense of justice!

147
00:05:54,000 --> 00:06:01,000
(Police car siren)

148
00:05:54,000 --> 00:06:01,000
(fire engine siren)

149
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:04,000
(Yokomine) Please stand back!

150
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:04,000
(camera shutter sound)

151
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:07,000
(Madashi Maruta)

152
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:07,000
Isn't there a driver who reported it?

153
00:06:07,000 --> 00:06:09,000
(Tachikawa) Ah. I can't find it.

154
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:12,000
Yokohama Minato from Kannai Higashi PB.

155
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:16,000
Directive No. 1285 has arrived and on-site regulations have begun.

156
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:19,000
The driver who caused the accident fled.

157
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:19,000
Please support us as soon as possible.

158
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:22,000
(Shibukawa) Chest deformity. I'll touch it.

159
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:25,000
Possible rib fractures and internal organ damage.

160
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:29,000
(Hanamaki) Is it okay?

161
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:29,000
Others were also refused...

162
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:31,000
is that so. Understood.

163
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:33,000
Captain Wangan Hospital!?

164
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:36,000
The cardiac surgeon on duty

165
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:36,000
I'm refusing to accept it.

166
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:38,000
(Male) Wow! Awesome!

167
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:40,000
Wow! Aww!

168
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:40,000
Oh no!

169
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:42,000
(Male) Real accident!

170
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:42,000
(Yokomine) Do whatever you want!

171
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:46,000
People's lives are at stake!

172
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:46,000
What are you going to do by taking a photo of it?

173
00:06:46,000 --> 00:06:48,000
Sorry, sorry! Sorry!

174
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:51,000
Officer, you said something good!

175
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:51,000
(Yokomine) Wait a minute…! No! Without permission.

176
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:55,000
I'm a lifesaving doctor.

177
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:57,000
Ah...? Huh! Hey... hey!

178
00:06:58,000 --> 00:07:01,000
Can you touch the radius?

179
00:06:58,000 --> 00:07:01,000
Please tell me about the patient's condition!

180
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:03,000
What is it!?

181
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:06,000
(Shibukawa) The radius is weak.

182
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:06,000
Trauma to the head and chest.

183
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:08,000
My airway is blocked. Let's intubate the trachea.

184
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:10,000
I mean, who are you!?

185
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:13,000
I am a specialist doctor at Wangan Hospital.

186
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:13,000
What is the patient's name?

187
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:15,000
This is Mr. Yamashiro.

188
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:20,000
Mr. Yamashiro! Mr. Yamashiro, can you hear me!?

189
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:20,000
Mr. Yamashiro, we'll take care of it right away.

190
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:23,000
Who will accept it?

191
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:23,000
(Hanamaki) It hasn't been decided yet.

192
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:30,000
Please carry it home.

193
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:30,000
I'll take care of it.

194
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:32,000
Let's go!

195
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:44,000
♬〜

196
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:46,000
(Mie) Patient

197
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:46,000
It appears that his heartbeat resumed during transport.

198
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:48,000
Are you ready?

199
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:51,000
(Hanamaki) Yes, okay!

200
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:54,000
Let's move it! I'll go with 3!

201
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:54,000
(Together) 1 2 3!

202
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:57,000
(Shibukawa) I'll get an AED.

203
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:57,000
(Nasu) Stretcher moves.

204
00:07:57,000 --> 00:08:00,000
(Hanamaki) Be careful with the code.

205
00:07:57,000 --> 00:08:00,000
(Nasu) I'll ask you more!

206
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:03,000
(Mie) Bring a thoracotomy set and disinfect it.

207
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:05,000
(Yuki Kuda) I'll take out the equipment.

208
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:05,000
(Momoyama) Then I'll go around the outside.

209
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:09,000
How are you doing, patient?

210
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:09,000
(Mie) Haruki Sensei: You can't do it alone.

211
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:12,000
No, this guy is a specialized doctor, but he's very skilled.

212
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:15,000
It's difficult to be too honest about your emotions.

213
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:15,000
(Mie) That's it.

214
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:18,000
Mr. Sachi, what are your vitals?

215
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:18,000
(Lucky) JCS200 Blood pressure is 70.

216
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:22,000
yes. Disinfect.

217
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:22,000
(Mie) Wait a minute! Inspect before disinfecting!

218
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:24,000
I know!

219
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:26,000
Haruka-chan, how is your mental health?

220
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:31,000
It's just a little messy...!

221
00:08:31,000 --> 00:08:33,000
(Mie) Idiot! Collect it!

222
00:08:31,000 --> 00:08:33,000
yes! Sorry!

223
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:36,000
Momoyama I'm leaving.

224
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:36,000
(Mie) Yes.

225
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:42,000
♬〜

226
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:44,000
Pulse check.

227
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:44,000
(light) Yes.

228
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:48,000
My heartbeat is restarting.

229
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:51,000
For the moment, my heart started beating.

230
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:54,000
(Daughter) Grandpa was saved!

231
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:56,000
Thank you, Mr. (Grandson).

232
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:58,000
Whether it will recover remains to be seen.

233
00:08:58,000 --> 00:09:01,000
Mr. Aoyama

234
00:08:58,000 --> 00:09:01,000
Please keep a 12-lead electrocardiogram.

235
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:03,000
(light) Yes.

236
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:07,000
(Akira Takagi) Enough already!

237
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:07,000
Mr. Haruki, give me a break!

238
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:10,000
If a mistake occurs, the hospital is responsible!

239
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:13,000
O-plus concentrated red blood cells 6 units

240
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:13,000
I brought it.

241
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:17,000
Yes, thank you.

242
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:17,000
Hey, if you're just complaining, why don't you leave it behind?

243
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:19,000
Enough already...!

244
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:23,000
Oh... I'm bleeding so badly.

245
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:23,000
Haruka-chan, are you okay?

246
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:25,000
But I have no choice but to do it.

247
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:29,000
Don't hope for a miracle.

248
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:29,000
``There is no such thing as God's protection.''

249
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:35,000
♬〜

250
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:37,000
Female.

251
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:37,000
(Lucky) Female.

252
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:45,000
Kuronuma-san, you're such an unscrupulous teacher. Please pull me out!

253
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:45,000
(Yui) Yes!

254
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:48,000
(ECG monitor alarm)

255
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:48,000
Oops…!

256
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:52,000
I'll open my chest!

257
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:52,000
First of all, let's check the bleeding spot!

258
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:59,000
I'll replace you. I got cut while freaking out

259
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:59,000
Patients don't accumulate.

260
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:02,000
Mr. Kiryu...!

261
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:02,000
Female.

262
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:18,000
♬〜

